Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:48.95,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(120,200)}心诚则明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香 这回不会让你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定要死在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 直到最后一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是兄妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不愿意在这里被幽灵残忍的杀害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我不会让这种事情发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在那命运之下保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…由我来终结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那脆弱的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当强烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是直美吗 快回话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 直美！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 是我 我现在碰到了很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美 让我听听你的声音 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你听不到我说话吗 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 随便说点什么就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妈妈啊 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个案件有一个女孩得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎幸子 这不就是刚刚那个女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是奇怪 她并没有被杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么变成幽灵存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好担心由香 说不定她现在还跟那孩子呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,录像带 取材记录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是最近的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有笔记本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎幸子的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生还方法 逆打法笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不就是回到原来世界的方法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就到你那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 喂 你哥哥不就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香 我可爱的妹妹呦 你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是个好孩子哟 由香 到我这来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你 杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你哟 由香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关住了吗 明明找到了回去的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么甘心在这止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着啊 由香 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为重要的人担心的那一份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有因此受到的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是死者与生者都可以无差别地得到的美丽的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在这里死去的人的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福和不幸是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想硬要得到幸福的话 是要承担相应的风险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们之所以会被困在这所学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为「幸福的幸子」咒语失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人默念的次数多了或者少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没按照人数正确地默念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 确实应该是默念九次的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能没弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一起念的朋友又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友之中的某个人觉得麻烦随便念了两下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者某个人还想继续寻刺激 不想这么简单地结束而故意失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是故意的 态度不正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以考虑在失败里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着「没关系 不会露馅的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有料到会有这么恐怖的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业病又犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就考虑各种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像还拿着咒语的碎片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请随时将其握紧 千万不要松开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你重要的人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心的情绪 扰乱内心的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓咒语 就是人之间相互的想法和感情 也就是人之内心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱恨皆可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思念越强烈 咒语的力量也越强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰我们是不可饶恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在痛苦中永生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 到你思念之人的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能有些晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏过去了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.32,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,「年糕小豆汤 在这边哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这里不是我们的教室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎 篠崎 振作一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！篠崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸…岸沼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲志和结衣老师他们呢 没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还没结束？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼！ 别过来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是在这样一个雨天放学后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被绑架的那天早上和妈妈吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想看见妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后我并没有回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是呆呆地蹲在走廊上 眺望着雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 义雄老师坐到我旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边听着我说话 一边「嗯嗯」地回应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师虽然得了不能说话的病 但却是个心地善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经也很喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 姐姐 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你就是管乃雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让被杀的我们成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么你在这里啊 不是已经成佛了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被割下来的舌头也还回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让穷凶极恶的犯人忏悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够啊…犯人的忏悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指那个文化人偶的忏悔不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要一波又一波的把无关人员都关起来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们拉到那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们这些小孩的幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仅仅是维持异空间的一个齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那杀了很多人了吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 姑且听下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有姐姐你们 但能平安回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然就用起关心的口吻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残留着强烈的迷恋 被强行剥夺了生命的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说他们相对于一般人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停留在了一种近乎错乱的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而 各种各样的感情和与思念掺杂在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 她说的都是真心话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 拜托了 把其他活着的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田和老师们也带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是诅咒力量变弱 趁着这个空当才回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 由于失去了悲伤情感的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的灵体 都开始丧失他们最后的一丝理性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也又会变成无差别攻击活人的怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他能救出持田同学他们的方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到那个地方 让我们都成佛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去齿轮的异空间 大概就会消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要回去吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 刚才为什么不说清楚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想知道的话 我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎！！ 篠崎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该晕过去了 却还有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但眼前一片漆黑 身体也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间 没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要遮我眼睛 给我拿下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！！！ 好疼 好疼啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 不要啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到我了…吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊 快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔出来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎！！篠崎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 篠崎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个就是那时的情景再现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害…这些孩子的…犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把犯人弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才附身小雪 然后被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手的照片和名字就刊登在先前的旧报纸上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身穿红衣的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎幸子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把同龄的孩子拐来 还进行了监禁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然老师才是犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳堀义雄只是从犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子被幸子杀害的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他蹲在房间的角落发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他为何要协助犯罪 目前还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要赶快告诉持田同学他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果毫无防备的与幸子接触会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那个空间的七星同学也不知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不赶快通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会在知道真相之前被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我再带进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会让你和其他的孩子成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不建议这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐以及其他人的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那个空间产生了强烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们选择回去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将无法再次将姐姐你们顺利地带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真打算回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 岸沼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种地方我不会再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼同学？…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再回去可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可能就真的死里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 自己苟且偷生就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是说场面话的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想死吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也担心哲志他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不该问你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不敢相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道就不想救救朋友吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是很危险 但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是持田同学的话一定会选择去救人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这无情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田同学他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾别人的感受？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想救大家 而只是想救持田吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田！ 持田！ 持田！ 持田！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 无所谓 我管你喜欢谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么那么说？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心的当然不只是持田君一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人也好 把我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且告诉你…岸沼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是很害怕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉到哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太黑的 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手机照个亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直就是独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 这是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是直美的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面有谁在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 直美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 早点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲志 哲志！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脚受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子给我包了绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在不在一起了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世以子…世以子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架分开后就成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见面的话 就把脖子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连道歉的机会都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原状态一定也不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲志…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原她也不是那种轻易放弃 然后自杀的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 筱原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很想带你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你在跟谁说话？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个小便女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你那肮脏的膀胱挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先藏在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然感觉冷飕飕的 但也比湿着强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 由香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.12,0:23:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原同…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个校服是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森繁同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲志 我没关系的 快去由香那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香会用怎样的声音哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 这就要完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.37,0:24:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一下 马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼同学 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.30,0:24:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼同学！…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.94,0:25:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑！ 篠崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.55,0:25:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走！！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.80,0:25:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了谁才回来的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.98,0:25:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.98,0:25:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岸沼同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.96,0:25:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快走！！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.72,0:25:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠崎 由香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.81,0:25:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.94,0:25:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良树？！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.63,0:25:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 篠崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.59,0:26:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由香…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.50,0:26:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…用…管…我...
